=========================================
  CDBx - CDB Reimplementation for Python
=========================================

CDBx is `CDB`_ reimplementation for Python.

Supported python versions are Python 2.7 and Python 3.6+.

.. _CDB: https://cr.yp.to/cdb.html


Development Status
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Beta.

~~~~
